casebody.head_matter:
In the Matter of DISCIPLINE OF Stephen E. CARTER.
No. D-2886.
Supreme Court of the United States
March 21, 2016.
Stephen E. Carter, of Beaufort, South Carolina, is suspended from the practice of law in this Court and a rule will issue, returnable within 40 days, requiring him to show cause why he should not be disbarred from the practice of law in this Court.
